config.script:
logger = system.util.getLogger('editWorkOrder')
	queryPath = "app/Schedule/editWorkOrder"
	
	params = {
		"workOrderName": self.view.custom.ExistingWorkOrder,
		"workOrderID": self.view.custom.ID,
		"quantity": self.view.custom.Quantity,
		"closed": self.view.custom.Closed,
		"hide": self.view.custom.Hide,
		"productCodeID": self.view.custom.ProductCode,
		"requiredEndDate": self.view.custom.RequiredEndDate
	}
	system.perspective.print(params)
	try:
		system.db.runNamedQuery(queryPath, params)
		system.perspective.sendMessage("addedWorkOrder")
		system.perspective.closePopup(self.view.params.ModalName)
	except Exception as e:
		logger.warn(e)
